OL,3,C'Not justified': Thousands of
OL,4,Cgovernment credit cards to be cancelled
OL,6,FThousands of government credit cards
OL,7,Fwill be cancelled this week, under
OL,8,Fplans to cut spending and ensure every
OL,9,Fpound of taxpayer money is targeted at
OL,10,Fdelivering for the public.
OL,12,FThe Cabinet Office will instruct
OL,13,Fdepartments and their agencies to
OL,14,Ffreeze almost all of the around 20,000
OL,15,FGovernment Procurement Cards in
OL,16,Fcirculation.
