OL,3,C'Not justified': Thousands of
OL,4,Cgovernment credit cards to be cancelled
OL,6,FThey say thousands of credit cards,
OL,7,Facross all departments, will be
OL,8,Fcancelled, under plans to cut spending
OL,9,Fand ensure budgets are more targeted
OL,10,Fat delivering for the public.
OL,12,FCardholders will then be forced to
OL,13,Freapply in a tougher new application
OL,14,Fprocess, with departments told to
OL,15,Fapprove the minimum number of new
OL,16,Fcards possible.
OL,18,FIt is expected the number of cards
OL,19,Fwill be reduced by at least 50%.
