OL,3,C'Not justified': Thousands of
OL,4,Cgovernment credit cards to be cancelled
OL,6,FOnly a minority of cards, used for
OL,7,Fspecific operational purposes such as
OL,8,Fby diplomatic staff working in
OL,9,Funstable environments, will be exempt
OL,10,Ffrom the mass freeze.
OL,12,FChancellor of the Duchy of Lancaster
OL,13,FPat McFadden, who ordered a review of
OL,14,Fthe cards, said: "We must ensure
OL,15,Ftaxpayers' money is spent on improving
OL,16,Fthe lives of working people.
