OL,3,C'Not justified': Thousands of
OL,4,Cgovernment credit cards to be cancelled
OL,6,F"It's not right that hundreds of
OL,7,Fmillions of pounds are spent on
OL,8,Fgovernment credit cards each year,
OL,9,Fwithout high levels of scrutiny or
OL,10,Fchallenge. Only officials for whom it
OL,11,Fis absolutely essential should have a
OL,12,Fcard."
OL,14,FThis follows the Prime Minister's
OL,15,Fintervention last week where he said
OL,16,Fthe Government must go "further and
OL,17,Ffaster" to reshape the state and make
OL,18,Fit work for working people.
